-- No Opel deal with Fiat or Magna soon: sources
-- 
-- Thu Apr 23, 2009 10:39am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/04/23/us-opel-suitors-sb-idUSTRE53M31120090423

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - Fiat ( FIA.MI ) and Magna Steyr MGa.TO are both interested in taking a stake in General Motors' ( GM.N ) struggling Opel unit, but a deal is not imminent, two sources close to the situation said on Thursday. 

 Fiat and Magna declined to comment. (Reporting by  Philipp Halstrick  and Patricia Uhlig; Writing by  Michael Shields )